UNOFFICIAL COPY 26 RS BR 1665
1 two brothers, Leighton (Amy) Dale and Nolan Dale and his fiancé, Syd Petonic;
2 cherished nieces, Libby Tate and Edie James Dale; aunts and uncles, David and Becky
3 Ginn, Tim and Sonya Ginn, Dianne Lee, Lisa and Doug Steele, Pam and Barry Albright,
4 and Bruce and Deb Dale; many beloved cousins; and her constant four-legged
5 companion, Henry;
6 NOW, THEREFORE,
7 Be it resolved by the Senate of the General Assembly of the Commonwealth of
8 Kentucky:
9 Section 1. The Senate hereby extends its most profound sympathy upon the
10 passing of Tatum Elizabeth Dale and expresses heartfelt condolences to her family and
11 community in this time of loss.
12 Section 2. When the Senate adjourns this day, it does so in honor and loving
13 memory of Tatum Elizabeth Dale.
14 Section 3. The Clerk of the Senate is directed to transmit a copy of this
15 Resolution to Senator Greg Elkins for delivery to the family.
